{"tid":799491,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 有冇人可以解釋到呢單靈異事件?","createTime":"2018-08-30T06:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T11:49:54.000Z","uid":45627,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eccb50e5743ed7659fdc318c9b5272ed223ba921","tid":799491,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"我今朝如常返工，大約九點鬆啲喺太子轉線去荃灣方向<br />\n上到車後我行近對面門企咗喺紅圈嘅位置，而紅圈前面嘅座位係有人坐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/135616_fa4e39031703565ca7b7e53334c537cf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F135616_fa4e39031703565ca7b7e53334c537cf.JPG&h=06d52a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開車後我繼續打機，打咗無耐抬頭一望我竟然喺深水埗去緊太子<br />\n我即刻望錶，時間係九點廿八分左右<br />\n<br />\n一開始以為自己掛住打機飛晒站，但冷靜後諗：<br />\n1. 廿五分鐘應該唔夠來回荃灣線 (仲未計停喺架車總站等嘅時間)<br />\n2. 成程車我冇聽到任何去到荃灣總站嘅廣播<br />\n3. 我前面個位一直都有人坐住，肯定冇換人<br />\n4. 冇人趕我落車亦冇感覺到有大批人落車／上車<br />\n5. 好肯定架車冇出過室外，因為荔景之後應該係室外路線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fddd3e60bbf123ea41b78925c098918bcf65055","tid":799491,"uid":72831,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:04:53.000Z","msg":"你未訓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0215ca4c12672a3ab9044bfd61d091fdaebb3aa","tid":799491,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"在這世界哪一個時空 可跟你往日重逢"},{"pid":"c1dea4abb2d64395b5e30a112e3c8f4fbe6ef497","tid":799491,"uid":73095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_tBciMX9Ajd4/S9Csfr2NfOI/AAAAAAAAALk/rxlwiVeWthg/s1600/Fringe.2x18.White.Tulip.HDTV.XviD-LOL.[tvu.org.